data.title: [1508521049] Truffle Hunt at Gordon Ramsay Restaurants to Win a Trip to Italy
data.description:

To enter, simply post a picture of a truffle dish you enjoyed at a @gordonramsay restaurant with the #GRGTruffleHunt hashtag on Twitter!
